Dialogue: 0,00:02:12.95,00:02:17.29,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}被命运捉弄  I’m falling down
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.56,00:02:22.69,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你同奏的和声  再也不会响起
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.76,00:02:27.89,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你强烈的香气还在心头萦绕
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.67,00:02:31.02,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不愿再继续等待
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.49,00:02:34.24,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Hey guess who’s back
Dialogue: 0,00:02:34.57,00:02:37.86,op1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}带着愿望
